title: Chile Core Consumer Prices
description: Core Consumer Prices in Chile increased to 121.23 points in October from 120.70 points in September of 2022. Core Consumer Prices in Chile averaged 63.38 points from 1978 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 121.23 points in October of 2022 and a record low of 2.96 points in December of 1978. This page provides - Chile Core Consumer Prices - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Institute of Statistics, Chile
